Parkinson’s disease (see 
                           WARNINGS, Neurological Adverse Reactions in Patients with Parkinson’s Disease or Dementia with Lewy Bodies
                        ).

Dementia with Lewy bodies (see 
                           WARNINGS, Neurological Adverse Reactions in Patients with Parkinson’s Disease or Dementia with Lewy Bodies
